column4: BlackBerry  Qualcomm decide on final amount to resolve royalty dispute
column5: May 26 Canada's BlackBerry Ltd said on Friday that U.S. chipmaker Qualcomm Inc has agreed to pay the software maker $940 million  including interest and legal fees  to settle a royalty dispute.
